original_title: Astaire and Rogers Sing the Great American Songbook
overview: Compilation of memorable songs from the Great American Songbook sung by Fred Astaire and Ginger Rogers in their films. Includes songs written by George and Ira Gershwin, Irving Berlin, Jerome Kern and Dorothy Fields, and Harold Arlen and Johnny Mercer.
title: Astaire and Rogers Sing the Great American Songbook
